The smearing of Rachel Jeantel So why is the star witness in the George Zimmerman case being treated like a defendant?

Rachel Jeantel is a 19-year-old Florida woman. On Facebook and Twitter, she's been known to post photos of her nails and talk about drinking. She is also the last person to have spoken with Trayvon Martin before George Zimmerman shot him to death last year, the woman who was on the phone with him when his fateful encounter unfolded.
